name: Autumn of NFTART SPECIAL 2 - NINJA ROBBOT -
description:
This NFT will be distributed to those who collect at least 4 NFTs (excluding specials) with "Autumn of NFTART" in the title!

In Japan, the autumn season is from September to November. Due to its comfortable climate, it is often called "Autumn of Art" because you can relax and enjoy art.
Today, I made this work to spread it to the world as the "autumn of NFT art".

I want to spread NFT art more! With that in mind, I MINT this work!
I really want you to enjoy the charm of NFT and spread it to your friends!
